00:10:27,709 --> 00:10:30,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 一个人起不了什么作用 所以没做什么</font>

152
00:10:31,149 --> 00:10:34,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且他们似乎也不重视我这种小人物</font>

153
00:10:35,079 --> 00:10:39,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你小子真无情 反正死人说不了话吗？</font>

154
00:10:42,109 --> 00:10:42,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好疼</font>

155
00:10:43,119 --> 00:10:44,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你干什么</font>

156
00:10:44,899 --> 00:10:46,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">下意识动脚了</font>

157
00:10:47,079 --> 00:10:48,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说…</font>

158
00:10:48,929 --> 00:10:51,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 她是风靡小姐</font>

159
00:10:53,579 --> 00:10:54,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我是加濑风靡</font>

160
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:57,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">她是警察吧？</font>

161
00:10:58,369 --> 00:11:03,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是警部补 我本来就是要带你去见她的</font>

162
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:07,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">风靡 我要和你商量这个女人的事情</font>

163
00:11:07,819 --> 00:11:08,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 你的女人？</font>

164
00:11:09,119 --> 00:11:10,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是个人称</font>

165
00:11:11,289 --> 00:11:14,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">初次见面 我是夏凪渚</font>

166
00:11:15,479 --> 00:11:17,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">商量啊…</font>

167
00:11:18,009 --> 00:11:19,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么偏偏找我？</font>

168
00:11:20,389 --> 00:11:22,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我觉得找风靡小姐的话 应该能为她做些什么</font>

169
00:11:23,199 --> 00:11:26,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">白痴 我又能怎么着？</font>

170
00:11:26,629 --> 00:11:30,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">风靡小姐 你和普通的警察不一样</font>

171
00:11:30,689 --> 00:11:32,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不一样？不同在哪？</font>

172
00:11:33,509 --> 00:11:34,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">决心</font>

173
00:11:40,549 --> 00:11:43,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来如此 事情我明白了</font>

174
00:11:44,229 --> 00:11:48,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我可不是医生 你们找其他人去吧</font>

175
00:11:48,779 --> 00:11:51,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">求求你 我一定要…</font>

176
00:11:51,149 --> 00:11:51,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且</font>

177
00:11:53,229 --> 00:11:58,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我很忙的 之后还要去别墅那边一趟</font>

178
00:11:59,069 --> 00:11:59,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">别墅？</font>

179
00:12:02,259 --> 00:12:07,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 如果你们自己要跟在我后面的话</font>

180
00:12:07,539 --> 00:12:08,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我也管不着</font>

181
00:12:15,379 --> 00:12:16,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">听好了</font>

182
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:22,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我会去上面把剩下的工作做完 20分钟后回来 好好记住</font>

183
00:12:26,559 --> 00:12:27,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">明白了？</font>

184
00:12:28,049 --> 00:12:28,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好</font>

185
00:12:31,719 --> 00:12:34,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 君冢 虽然现在问这个有点太迟了…</font>

186
00:12:35,109 --> 00:12:37,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们不是要去别墅吗？</font>

187
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:40,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这里明显就是…</font>

188
00:12:40,779 --> 00:12:41,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是监狱哦</font>

189
00:12:42,229 --> 00:12:45,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦你个头啊 别墅在哪儿啊？</font>

190
00:12:45,989 --> 00:12:47,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这只是一种「黑话」！</font>

191
00:12:48,039 --> 00:12:49,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「喝一壶啊」？</font>

192
00:12:49,569 --> 00:12:51,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你真喝了一壶吗 脸都红了</font>

193
00:12:52,689 --> 00:12:55,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">该走了 我们的目的地…</font>

194
00:12:56,179 --> 00:12:57,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在最里面</font>

195
00:13:01,929 --> 00:13:03,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谁在里面？</font>

196
00:13:03,499 --> 00:13:04,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大叔</font>

197
00:13:04,599 --> 00:13:05,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">认真点</font>

198
00:13:05,979 --> 00:13:07,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不当人的大叔</font>

199
00:13:08,259 --> 00:13:09,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂！</font>

200
00:13:16,109 --> 00:13:17,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是令人怀念啊</font>

201
00:13:19,129 --> 00:13:20,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大侦探</font>

202
00:13:20,849 --> 00:13:23,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">很遗憾 我不是大侦探</font>

203
00:13:26,889 --> 00:13:27,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是…</font>

204
00:13:28,839 --> 00:13:30,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 是「华生」啊</font>

205
00:13:31,519 --> 00:13:33,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你眼睛还看得见吗？</font>

206
00:13:35,219 --> 00:13:35,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看不见了</font>

207
00:13:36,619 --> 00:13:39,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和有着一双死鱼眼的华生真是绝配</font>

208
00:13:40,349 --> 00:13:42,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那这可是本世纪最大的坏消息了</font>

209
00:13:43,289 --> 00:13:46,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还有 希望你不要这么叫我</font>

210
00:13:47,739 --> 00:13:50,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么 不玩助手游戏了吗？</font>

211
00:13:58,039 --> 00:14:00,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">今天我来这里是有话要和你说</font>

212
00:14:00,799 --> 00:14:06,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没什么特殊的事情 你们也不会跑到这种地方来见我</font>

213
00:14:06,769 --> 00:14:10,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就当是给我打发时间吧 说说看</font>

214
00:14:11,979 --> 00:14:12,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗</font>

215
00:14:14,779 --> 00:14:15,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么了？</font>

216
00:14:17,489 --> 00:14:21,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你很紧张啊 这可不符合你的性格</font>

217
00:14:21,789 --> 00:14:22,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说什么呢？</font>

218
00:14:27,219 --> 00:14:28,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">蝙蝠 我给你介绍一下</font>

219
00:14:29,679 --> 00:14:33,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">旁边这位女生叫夏凪渚 我的同年级同学</font>

220
00:14:34,359 --> 00:14:36,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪…渚？</font>

221
00:14:38,509 --> 00:14:41,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">初次见面 我是夏凪</font>

222
00:14:42,169 --> 00:14:47,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">今天我是来和您谈谈我的心脏的</font>

223
00:14:59,969 --> 00:15:05,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来如此 是对心脏的原主没有头绪吗</font>

224
00:15:06,499 --> 00:15:10,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是的 就是这样的…</font>

225
00:15:11,299 --> 00:15:14,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪 他的经历并不普通</font>

226
00:15:15,689 --> 00:15:16,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要说的话</font>

227
00:15:17,669 --> 00:15:19,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他甚至都不是普通的人类</font>

228
00:15:20,849 --> 00:15:25,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">蝙蝠是秘密组织「SPES」制造出来的人造人</font>

229
00:15:26,869 --> 00:15:27,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啊？</font>

230
00:15:28,229 --> 00:15:29,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你应该不会相信吧</font>

231
00:15:29,849 --> 00:15:32,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那当然了 这种蠢事怎么可能…</font>

232
00:15:32,649 --> 00:15:34,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">会有的哦</font>

233
00:15:35,079 --> 00:15:37,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">世界可是很大的</font>

234
00:15:40,349 --> 00:15:44,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只要我愿意 连100公里外的交谈声都能听清</font>

235
00:15:45,329 --> 00:15:49,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">分辨出你的心跳声更是小菜一碟</font>

236
00:15:50,029 --> 00:15:52,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他就是凭借这个来往于各个国家</font>

237
00:15:53,199 --> 00:16:00,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以 也许他曾经遇到过你这个心脏的原主</font>

238
00:16:01,219 --> 00:16:06,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也没什么好瞒的 我对他非常了解</font>

239
00:16:06,739 --> 00:16:07,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看起来是了</font>

240
00:16:10,029 --> 00:16:14,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我和你们打的那一架 已经是4年前的事了吧</font>

241
00:16:15,579 --> 00:16:16,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「你们」？</font>

242
00:16:17,579 --> 00:16:19,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真令人怀念</font>

243
00:16:19,909 --> 00:16:24,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说 我不愿意被那耳朵听我心脏的声音啊</font>

244
00:16:25,249 --> 00:16:26,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个嘛…</font>

245
00:16:26,979 --> 00:16:31,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不不 听心脏的声音而已 这个距离已经够了</font>

246
00:16:32,179 --> 00:16:37,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说 其实我已经判断出小姑娘你的心脏是谁的了</font>

247
00:16:38,869 --> 00:16:45,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">蝙蝠 你真的遇到过夏凪心脏的原主？</font>

248
00:16:45,709 --> 00:16:47,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">与其啰啰嗦嗦地说明</font>

249
00:16:48,299 --> 00:16:50,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还是这样更方便</font>

250
00:16:55,579 --> 00:16:56,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是…</font>

251
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:06,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔！</font>

252
00:17:06,989 --> 00:17:11,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的触手再也不能攻击我了</font>

253
00:17:11,489 --> 00:17:14,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是与生俱来的大侦探体质</font>

254
00:17:17,449 --> 00:17:18,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">难道…</font>

255
00:17:19,259 --> 00:17:21,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么…怎么会这样…</font>

256
00:17:22,659 --> 00:17:23,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要…</font>

257
00:17:25,659 --> 00:17:26,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我已经…</font>

258
00:17:26,769 --> 00:17:30,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">华生 逃避现实就太可耻了</font>

259
00:17:32,339 --> 00:17:36,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我一开始还以为是那个女人来这里了呢</font>

260
00:17:39,689 --> 00:17:41,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是令人怀念啊</font>

261
00:17:42,699 --> 00:17:43,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大侦探</font>

262
00:17:46,009 --> 00:17:47,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是这样的吗…</font>

263
00:17:49,529 --> 00:17:51,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我就觉得奇怪</font>

264
00:17:51,999 --> 00:17:57,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我可不是第一次见到个男生就会拥抱上去的人啊</font>

265
00:17:58,479 --> 00:18:01,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以那样的行为 并不是我的想法</font>

266
00:18:02,079 --> 00:18:04,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而是出自这个心脏的原主</font>

267
00:18:05,099 --> 00:18:09,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">由你当助手的那个大侦探 名叫谢丝塔的女生</font>

268
00:18:11,189 --> 00:18:13,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪 你…</font>

269
00:18:18,669 --> 00:18:19,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">偶然而已</font>

270
00:18:21,059 --> 00:18:26,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和夏凪你认识 以及谢丝塔的心脏在你的体内</font>

271
00:18:26,989 --> 00:18:28,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一切都只是…</font>

272
00:18:35,289 --> 00:18:39,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这也是心脏原主的影响吗 夏凪</font>

273
00:18:39,639 --> 00:18:40,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不对！</font>

274
00:18:41,399 --> 00:18:45,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在是出于我的意志！因为我想打你就打了！</font>

275
00:18:46,429 --> 00:18:50,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说偶然？你说这样的重逢只是偶然？</font>

276
00:18:50,249 --> 00:18:54,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">开什么玩笑！别用偶然来解释！</font>

277
00:18:54,679 --> 00:18:55,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是她的心意！</font>

278
00:18:56,449 --> 00:19:00,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使死了 也想见到你 想和你在一起的心意！</font>

279
00:19:01,139 --> 00:19:04,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是这颗小小的心脏里蕴含的唯一心愿！</font>

280
00:19:05,479 --> 00:19:08,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们…我们一直…</font>

281
00:19:09,579 --> 00:19:12,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">都在找你啊 君冢君彦！</font>

282
00:19:13,599 --> 00:19:17,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要把这一切用偶然这种词来敷衍！</font>

283
00:19:18,329 --> 00:19:20,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不许侮辱别人的心意！</font>

284
00:19:27,319 --> 00:19:28,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你就在里面吗</font>

285
00:19:31,749 --> 00:19:36,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你知不知道 当你的助手 给我造成了多少麻烦</font>

286
00:19:37,399 --> 00:19:40,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">从和神秘组织的超自然大战开始</font>

287
00:19:40,769 --> 00:19:44,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">3年来为了摆脱对方的追杀 一直在全世界漫游</font>

288
00:19:45,269 --> 00:19:47,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为身无分文 就算刮着飓风也只能在野外露宿</font>

289
00:19:48,659 --> 00:19:50,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有时候在赌场里打工赚了点钱</font>

290
00:19:50,429 --> 00:19:52,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就兴奋地跑到度假区的酒店里 享受着弹性十足的大床</font>

291
00:19:53,559 --> 00:19:55,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">结果第二天又没钱了</font>

292
00:19:56,219 --> 00:20:00,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">走过沙漠 穿过森林 跨过山脉 渡过大海</font>

293
00:20:01,519 --> 00:20:03,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还有…还有…</font>

294
00:20:06,789 --> 00:20:10,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么就先我而死了啊 混蛋！</font>

295
00:20:25,859 --> 00:20:28,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有收获了吧 这是好事</font>

296
00:20:29,109 --> 00:20:30,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好好感谢我吧</font>

297
00:20:31,439 --> 00:20:34,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">风靡小姐 你早就全都知道了吧</font>

298
00:20:35,059 --> 00:20:35,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啥？</font>

299
00:20:37,039 --> 00:20:37,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">她…</font>

300
00:20:38,539 --> 00:20:42,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪的心脏到底来自谁 你其实一清二楚</font>

301
00:20:44,359 --> 00:20:44,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">风靡小姐</font>

302
00:20:53,079 --> 00:20:56,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我还不至于非要让这个小姑娘去当侦探</font>

303
00:21:05,309 --> 00:21:07,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">今天真是谢谢了</font>

304
00:21:07,589 --> 00:21:07,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">咦？</font>

305
00:21:08,959 --> 00:21:11,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">多亏了你 怎么说呢…</font>

306
00:21:13,199 --> 00:21:15,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 再这样浑浑噩噩下去是不行的</font>

307
00:21:17,619 --> 00:21:19,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真要这么说的话 我也…</font>

308
00:21:25,219 --> 00:21:25,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪</font>

309
00:21:27,209 --> 00:21:30,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不管那颗心脏是来自于谁</font>

310
00:21:31,739 --> 00:21:34,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也只需要过好你自己的人生</font>

311
00:21:37,789 --> 00:21:40,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不用想着去代替什么人</font>

312
00:21:44,029 --> 00:21:44,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">再见</font>

313
00:21:48,999 --> 00:21:49,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢</font>

314
00:21:50,409 --> 00:21:51,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我…</font>

315
00:21:53,339 --> 00:21:54,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么了 夏凪</font>

316
00:21:57,349 --> 00:21:58,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个…我！</font>

317
00:22:01,109 --> 00:22:04,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有件事想请大侦探帮我解决！</font>

318
00:22:06,509 --> 00:22:11,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">每次醒来 你都在我身边</font>

319
00:22:11,879 --> 00:22:17,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我一个全新的早晨</font>

320
00:22:17,029 --> 00:22:22,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心跳是如此温柔</font>

321
00:22:22,409 --> 00:22:27,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又悲伤得催人泪下</font>

322
00:22:27,729 --> 00:22:33,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在大声叫喊着 想要见到某人</font>

323
00:22:33,079 --> 00:22:38,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又不知道名字和长相</font>

324
00:22:38,409 --> 00:22:43,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我真的听到了那声音</font>

325
00:22:43,729 --> 00:22:48,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能漫无目的地去探寻</font>

326
00:22:48,689 --> 00:22:53,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然可能只会徒增烦恼</font>

327
00:22:54,029 --> 00:23:02,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这不是为了别人而是为了自己</font>

328
00:23:03,869 --> 00:23:09,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胸膛中的声音 那声呐喊 指引着我前进</font>

329
00:23:09,169 --> 00:23:14,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将零落的心意捡起 送到它想去的地方吧</font>

330
00:23:14,489 --> 00:23:19,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为是你告诉我生命的意义</font>

331
00:23:19,739 --> 00:23:27,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 这个世界也许还没那么坏</font>

332
00:23:36,009 --> 00:23:41,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">（第3集 这就是唯喵品质！）</font>

